ずっときれいですねえ

26
00:02:44.289 --> 00:02:48.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ああ いい香り！ お味噌の
香りであることに違いはないのに

27
00:02:48.543 --> 00:02:51.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
とても清々(すがすが)しくて爽やかで…

28
00:02:53.965 --> 00:02:55.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
えっ？

29
00:02:55.341 --> 00:02:56.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ…

30
00:02:56.301 --> 00:02:58.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
