33
00:03:18.364 --> 00:03:22.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
卵の黄身を味噌漬けしただけなのに
生臭くもなければ

34
00:03:22.201 --> 00:03:24.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
くどくもないだあ？ これが

35
00:03:24.454 --> 00:03:26.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
悔しい… が うまい

36
00:03:27.081 --> 00:03:30.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（谷村(たにむら)秀夫）まさに
玲瓏(れいろう)なること玉のごとき味だ

37
00:03:31.210 --> 00:03:32.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（大原(おおはら)大蔵）山岡…

38
00:03:35.131 --> 00:03:37.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
