217
00:14:02.132 --> 00:14:04.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フンッ 大口たたきおって

218
00:14:06.387 --> 00:14:10.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
フフフフフッ
ハハハハハハ…

