236
00:15:25.591 --> 00:15:28.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ… ハァ…

237
00:15:28.344 --> 00:15:30.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
